│ defined inside.                                                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ The problem is subtle. The PHIs `%res.iv1` and `%res.iv2` are *not* defined inside the loop. They are defined in the         │
│ `return` block, which is an exit block. They *use* a value from inside the loop (`%iv`).                                     │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ The fix seems to be in `VPlanTransforms::createVectorLoop`. When creating the exit from the vector loop, we need to          │
